name: f.r.a.g.m.e.n.t.s_memories
description:
an artistic capture of fragmented emotions and memories and how it feels like to feel confused and unavailable to remember when you're mentally & physcially protected from a painful experience. 

We hide ourselves, to protect ourselves. 
 
| a part of f.r.a.g.m.e.n.t.s series - each piece is limited to an edition of 1 | 

artist: @greyowlZ
